<h2>DiSC Trainer Certification &ndash; Public Course</h2>
<h2>Investment &pound;995.00&nbsp;</h2>
<p>This certification course is designed to provide the knowledge and content expertise you need to confidently answer questions and help build others&rsquo; understanding and application of DiSC.</p>
<p>You will receive comprehensive training that will equip you with the knowledge and resources to be confident in your ability to apply DiSC "practically" in any individual, team development, coaching, or training situation.</p>
<p>Importantly, the certification will provide you with the versatility to craft solutions and equip you to meet a wide variety of organisational needs.</p>
<p>On completion of the course you will be designated as a DiSC Certified Trainer.</p>
<h4>Who should get certified?&nbsp;</h4>
<p>Anyone in a training, coaching, consulting or people-development&nbsp;role who wishes to understand, utilise, and maximise the benefit of using Everything DiSC profiles within an organisation in order to:</p>
<ul>
<li>Improve communication, collaboration and reduce conflict.</li>
<li>Build results-producing teams.</li>
<li>Develop effective coaches and managers.</li>
<li>Increase sales and service success.&nbsp;</li>
</ul>
<p>As a DiSC Certified Trainer&nbsp;you will learn to be successful in your interaction with others by mastering validated and user friendly tools. More importantly the certification will provide you with new, unmatched versatility in crafting solutions for a wide variety of organisational issues.</p>
<h4>What&rsquo;s involved?</h4>
<p>DiSC Trainer Certification is a one day intensive classroom-based training&nbsp;event.</p>
<h4>During the day you will:&nbsp;</h4>
<ul>
<li>Become confident and competent when using Everything DiSC tools in any training, coaching, or consulting capacity.</li>
<li>Know the history of DiSC and the theory behind the DiSC model.</li>
<li>Understand personality and situational behaviour.</li>
<li>Understand and recognise behavioural styles.</li>
<li>Learn how to competently interpret DiSC Profiles and give meaningful and powerful feedback to respondents.</li>
</ul>
<h4>What are the Benefits?</h4>
<ul>
<li>Detailed understanding of the DiSC model and how to derive maximum benefit from the range of Everything DiSC tools.</li>
<li>Access to a selection of off-the-shelf DiSC based Training Systems which can be tailored to address any challenge, whether it be general communication or a specific application such as management, leadership or sales.</li>
<li>Ability to administer, manage and interpret Everything DiSC profiles so that you can add huge value to your clients&rsquo; understanding of themselves, those around them and their ability to communicate more effectively.</li>
Immediate access to your own online EPIC portal where you will have full control of administration and access to our full suite of online profiles and follow up reports.</ul>
